{"tid":486793,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"［音響撚］HDMI ARC 問題求救","createTime":"2017-12-02T07:12:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-05T10:50:42.000Z","uid":45229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e0f1da5a3b82bc431e2faf877a0c5bf5d87c58e1","tid":486793,"uid":45229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T07:12:19.000Z","msg":"是咁的，近日入手左Sony x9000e同Onkyo 575e<br />\n<br />\n本身諗住用ARC出聲睇電視/Netflix。頭一日set好左都無問題<br />\n<br />\n今日問題黎喇，打完機轉番去睇電視個ARC就唔work無左聲了，最後要重新disable enable過TV個ARC setting先有番聲。想問下有無巴打預過同樣情況？"},{"pid":"28a7dedf535fd8e9e47334a66fbd77fbcec9b080","tid":486793,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T07:19:19.000Z","msg":"我都係，<br />\n電視lg, <br />\n5.1喇叭飛利浦<br />\n<br />\n條hdmi線經常唔得，<br />\n明明set好哂。<br />\n<br />\n但如果<br />\n用手提電腦駁喇叭，<br />\n喇叭再駁電視，<br />\n電視又可以用番hdmi arc,<br />\n出到hdmi聲音畫面。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b8b444d20251540ce611bb792b0528ad1381c49","tid":486793,"uid":45229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T07:22:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係，<br />\n電視lg, <br />\n5.1喇叭飛利浦<br />\n<br />\n條hdmi線經常唔得，<br />\n明明set好哂。<br />\n<br />\n但如果<br />\n用手提電腦駁喇叭，<br />\n喇叭再駁電視，<br />\n電視又可以用番hdmi arc,<br />\n出到hdmi聲音畫面。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真心想知咩問題，我search外國好人都有同樣問題。<br />\n唔想次次打完機睇完dvd，轉番TV Channel都要set過曬d ARC setting<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb70b74263669e04920e84a253922a115dae4fa","tid":486793,"uid":45229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T07:28:04.000Z","msg":"我個setting係咁的<br />\n<br />\nOnkyo (HDMI ARC) &lt;---&gt; Sony TV (HDMI ARC)<br />\nOnkyo (HDMI 1) &lt;---&gt; PS4<br />\nOnkyo (HDMI 2) &lt;---&gt; BD Player<br />\nOnkyo (HDMI 3) &lt;---&gt; NowTV<br />\nOnkyo (HDMI 4) &lt;---&gt; Switch <br />\n<br />\n總之次次用完HDMI 1-4後轉番去睇電視個ARC就會傻左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ad18717a51b11455e2e5b4d0529a6d480536596","tid":486793,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T07:28:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係，<br />\n電視lg, <br />\n5.1喇叭飛利浦<br />\n<br />\n條hdmi線經常唔得，<br />\n明明set好哂。<br />\n<br />\n但如果<br />\n用手提電腦駁喇叭，<br />\n喇叭再駁電視，<br />\n電視又可以用番hdmi arc,<br />\n出到hdmi聲音畫面。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你呢個setting已經冇用到arc(好似係)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c394a0d3efd25bf95dee9389fe025814ccf763","tid":486793,"uid":45229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T08:22:37.000Z","msg":"Upgrade埋onkyo個firmware, 都係一樣情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09bf5fb0481bf00650de7524cca20ee8da99081","tid":486793,"uid":46974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T08:25:05.000Z","msg":"Arc極on9 <br />\n建議買條optical 一了百了，又可以出到Dolby Digital Plus"},{"pid":"6e3a3473feb7d8908ee0f622b8a83c1ac554af8f","tid":486793,"uid":45229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T08:31:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Arc極on9 <br />\n建議買條optical 一了百了，又可以出到Dolby Digital Plus</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nYes, 真係好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家想放棄買optical算"},{"pid":"f4971c1d1998ca9d0da89aab3dc696386642da97","tid":486793,"uid":45229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T11:03:18.000Z","msg":"ARC唯一可取係開電視佢識幫你開埋部amp，熄機又係"},{"pid":"154e3e739d789a4a3ed284e79444f0de7be4f3f7","tid":486793,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T13:50:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Arc極on9 <br />\n建議買條optical 一了百了，又可以出到Dolby Digital Plus</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nYes, 真係好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家想放棄買optical算</blockquote><br />\n我hdmi arc/ 光纖都插哂，<br />\nhdmi用唔到即刻用光纖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a1320031cf1ae89f12e6921f53fd9e25ab16fb9","tid":486793,"uid":28168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T01:55:31.000Z","msg":"有冇試過另一條hdmi?<br />\n一樣9000e + amp hdmi arc, PS4+appletv+電腦+mytv轉黎轉去都冇事"},{"pid":"5f36bebb55cf1adecf1092f6b432e29f9a87e8e3","tid":486793,"uid":78994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T03:57:23.000Z","msg":"我用緊w700c 同 nr1607 , hdmi arc 電視, 其餘ps4 pc ps3 一樣點轉都無事<br />\n我只係用緊taobao D (應該係正貨)prolink hdmi 線"},{"pid":"cde03ce35e491a3c478b323113ae7f1e1a4dd7bb","tid":486793,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T10:04:33.000Z","msg":"ARC不嬲垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28db7c29efe706b111cee68cd001fd0e250f827f","tid":486793,"uid":15793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T10:50:42.000Z","msg":"有得攪，google &ldquo;HDMI CEC problem pin 13&rdquo;"}]}